titles.title: An original bill to provide for a temporary increase in the public debt limit.

action.text: Committee on Finance. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Moynihan. Without written report.

calendar.text: Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 55.

action.text: Indefinitely postponed by Senate by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: 4/2/1993--Introduced. Provides for a temporary increase in the public debt limit.
